highlights.text: “The Highs & The Lows (feat. Joey BadA$$)” by Chance the Rapper and Joey Bada$$ is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs USA, up 24 spots at #31.
“Pelotero A La Bola” by 8Uno and Airam Paez has been on Viral Songs USA the longest, at 73 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs USA. “Golden” is the highest at #3.
“The Happy Song” by Imogen Heap is the highest new entry on Viral Songs USA at #79.
